DEFINE
	VAR __DS0Core = 
		SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
			'Adv_Works_Product Categories Lookup'[CategoryName],
			"Total_Orders_SalesPerCust", 'Measure_Table (Sales)'[Total_Orders_SalesPerCust]
		)

	VAR __DS0PrimaryWindowed = 
		TOPN(
			1001,
			__DS0Core,
			[Total_Orders_SalesPerCust],
			0,
			'Adv_Works_Product Categories Lookup'[CategoryName],
			1
		)

EVALUATE
	__DS0PrimaryWindowed

ORDER BY
	[Total_Orders_SalesPerCust] DESC,
	'Adv_Works_Product Categories Lookup'[CategoryName]

DEFINE
	VAR __DS0Core = 
		SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
			'Adv_Wrks Calendar Lookup'[Start of Week],
			"Total_Cost", 'Measure_Table (Sales)'[Total Cost]
		)

	VAR __DS0IntersectionCount = CALCULATE(COUNTROWS(__DS0Core))

	VAR __DS0BodyBinnedSample = 
		SAMPLEAXISWITHLOCALMINMAX(
			3500,
			__DS0Core,
			'Adv_Wrks Calendar Lookup'[Start of Week],
			[Total_Cost],
			350,
			,
			ALPHABETICAL,
			ASC,
			105000,
			60
		)

EVALUATE
	ROW(
	"DS0IntersectionCount", __DS0IntersectionCount
)

EVALUATE
	__DS0BodyBinnedSample

ORDER BY
	'Adv_Wrks Calendar Lookup'[Start of Week]

DEFINE
	VAR __SQDS0Core = 
		SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
			'Adv_Wrks_Product Subcategories Lookup'[SubcategoryName],
			"Total_Orders_SalesPerCust", 'Measure_Table (Sales)'[Total_Orders_SalesPerCust]
		)

	VAR __SQDS0BodyLimited = 
		TOPN(1, __SQDS0Core, [Total_Orders_SalesPerCust], 0)

EVALUATE
	SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
		__SQDS0BodyLimited,
		"MinSubcategoryName", IGNORE(CALCULATE(MIN('Adv_Wrks_Product Subcategories Lookup'[SubcategoryName])))
	)

DEFINE
	VAR __DS0Core = 
		SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
			'Adv_Wrks Calendar Lookup'[Start of Month],
			"CountCaps_Short_Month", CALCULATE(COUNTA('Adv_Wrks Calendar Lookup'[Caps_Short_Month])),
			"Total_Cost", 'Measure_Table (Sales)'[Total Cost]
		)

	VAR __DS0BodyLimited = 
		TOPN(1002, __DS0Core, 'Adv_Wrks Calendar Lookup'[Start of Month], 0)

EVALUATE
	__DS0BodyLimited

ORDER BY
	'Adv_Wrks Calendar Lookup'[Start of Month]

DEFINE
	VAR __DS0Core = 
		SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
			'Adv_Wrks Calendar Lookup'[Start of Month],
			"CountPrefix", CALCULATE(COUNTA('Adv_Wrks_Customer Lookup'[Prefix])),
			"Total_Orders_SalesPerCust", 'Measure_Table (Sales)'[Total_Orders_SalesPerCust]
		)

	VAR __DS0BodyLimited = 
		TOPN(1002, __DS0Core, 'Adv_Wrks Calendar Lookup'[Start of Month], 0)

EVALUATE
	__DS0BodyLimited

ORDER BY
	'Adv_Wrks Calendar Lookup'[Start of Month]

DEFINE
	VAR __DS0Core = 
		SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
			'Adv_Wrks Calendar Lookup'[Start of Month],
			"CountPrefix", CALCULATE(COUNTA('Adv_Wrks_Customer Lookup'[Prefix])),
			"Total_Return_QTY_explict_Return_calc_Measure", 'Measure_Table (Sales)'[Total Return_QTY_explict_Return_calc_Measure]
		)

	VAR __DS0BodyLimited = 
		TOPN(1002, __DS0Core, 'Adv_Wrks Calendar Lookup'[Start of Month], 0)

EVALUATE
	__DS0BodyLimited

ORDER BY
	'Adv_Wrks Calendar Lookup'[Start of Month]

DEFINE
	VAR __SQDS0Core = 
		SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
			'Adv_Wrks_Product Lookup'[ProductName],
			"Total_Orders_SalesPerCust", 'Measure_Table (Sales)'[Total_Orders_SalesPerCust]
		)

	VAR __SQDS0BodyLimited = 
		TOPN(10, __SQDS0Core, [Total_Orders_SalesPerCust], 0)

	VAR __DS0Core = 
		SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
			'Adv_Wrks_Product Lookup'[ProductName],
			__SQDS0BodyLimited,
			"Total_Cost", 'Measure_Table (Sales)'[Total Cost],
			"Total_Customers", 'Measure_Table (Sales)'[Total_Customers],
			"Total_Return_QTY_explict_Return_calc_Measure", 'Measure_Table (Sales)'[Total Return_QTY_explict_Return_calc_Measure]
		)

	VAR __DS0PrimaryWindowed = 
		TOPN(501, __DS0Core, [Total_Cost], 0, 'Adv_Wrks_Product Lookup'[ProductName], 1)

EVALUATE
	GROUPBY(
		__DS0Core,
		"MinTotal_Customers", MINX(CURRENTGROUP(), [Total_Customers]),
		"MaxTotal_Customers", MAXX(CURRENTGROUP(), [Total_Customers]),
		"MinTotal_Return_QTY_explict_Return_calc_Measure", MINX(CURRENTGROUP(), [Total_Return_QTY_explict_Return_calc_Measure]),
		"MaxTotal_Return_QTY_explict_Return_calc_Measure", MAXX(CURRENTGROUP(), [Total_Return_QTY_explict_Return_calc_Measure]),
		"MinTotal_Cost", MINX(CURRENTGROUP(), [Total_Cost]),
		"MaxTotal_Cost", MAXX(CURRENTGROUP(), [Total_Cost])
	)

EVALUATE
	__DS0PrimaryWindowed

ORDER BY
	[Total_Cost] DESC, 'Adv_Wrks_Product Lookup'[ProductName]
